{"tid":1776964,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[浴火重生] MOMOLAND將於十二月底回歸","createTime":"2019-12-10T01:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T12:14:54.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7534deecdcce61f124b7c9c4d7c503a9210caba6","tid":1776964,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://kprofiles.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Momoland.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkprofiles.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2FMomoland.png&h=cd5cf723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/article/9d354fba20220301c64bee10d0b1b298f8119bf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farticle%2F9d354fba20220301c64bee10d0b1b298f8119bf1.jpg&h=75525594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3003080/org/9662527aa2116a9445907f36b90dc678.jpg/TQiithfLAb6gwrrxX1ym4K3pUq4CAJobRltn7EZbZ-w?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3003080%2Forg%2F9662527aa2116a9445907f36b90dc678.jpg%2FTQiithfLAb6gwrrxX1ym4K3pUq4CAJobRltn7EZbZ-w%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d238c5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n組合MOMOLAND在重組爲6人組後,將於12月底回歸。<br />\n<br />\n10日,根據《新聞1》的採訪結果,MOMOLAND 將於本月末以數位單曲回歸。此張專輯是成員妍雨和泰河,Daisy缺席後,以6人形式開始活動的首張專輯,預計將吸引粉絲們的關注。<br />\n<br />\nMOMOLAND此前展現出了活潑開朗的活力魅力。 重組爲6人組的她們將以怎樣的面貌站在舞臺上令人期待。<br />\n<br />\n上個月30日,MOMOLAND的所屬公司MLD Entertainment發佈了MOMOLAND將重組爲6人組的消息,&quot;MOMOLAND的成員泰河和妍雨小姐將離開組合,新的開始&quot;,&quot;泰河和妍雨在很長時間裏對本人的前途進行了充分的思考,並進行了這樣的思考&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n接著,公司還表示&quot;Daisy的情況還在相互協商中,在結束協商後會將消息轉達給大家&quot;。 所屬公司正在繼續討論Daisy的留隊問題,預計以後會表明立場。<br />\n<br />\nMOMOLAND2016年通過Mnet生存節目出道,通過《BBoom BBoom》,《BAAM》,《I&rsquo;m So Hot》等熱門歌曲獲得了大衆喜愛。"},{"pid":"85954d5c0825c13ca798dbd7d76268eb95f95f32","tid":1776964,"uid":213300,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"冇妍雨嘅